  <!-- PROJECTS -->
  <section class="section projects" id="projects">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-num">02</span>
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="project-grid">
 
        <article class="project-card featured">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-type">Electronics Lead</span>
              <span class="card-date">Aug 2025 – Present</span>
            </div>
            <span class="card-glyph">⚙</span>
          </div>
          <h3>UB ASME — IAM3D Rover</h3>
          <p>Leading full electronics integration for a 3D-printed rover competing against colleges on payload delivery. Designed a multi-battery power system for ~25% motor performance gain, programmed Arduino + ESP32 for RC control, and built a servo-actuated excavator scoop with FPV camera and laser alignment.</p>
          <ul class="card-tags">
            <li>Arduino</li><li>ESP32</li><li>Power Systems</li><li>FPV</li><li>3D Printing</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
 
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-type">Project</span>
              <span class="card-date">March 2026</span>
            </div>
            <span class="card-glyph">◎</span>
          </div>
          <h3>2-Axis Gimbal Stabilization</h3>
          <p>Designed and built a 2-axis gimbal for FPV camera stabilization using servo motors and RC control. PID control loops on Arduino minimize angular error. Custom 3D-printed frame optimized for low rotational inertia and balanced center of mass.</p>
          <ul class="card-tags">
            <li>PID Control</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Servo Motors</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
 
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-type">Project</span>
              <span class="card-date">February 2026</span>
            </div>
            <span class="card-glyph">△</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Self-Balancing Inverted Pendulum</h3>
          <p>Fully 3D-printed two-wheel inverted pendulum with closed-loop PID control via IMU-based tilt estimation. Characterized transient response through step-disturbance testing, tuning gains to minimize overshoot and settling time.</p>
          <ul class="card-tags">
            <li>PID Control</li><li>IMU</li><li>C++</li><li>Control Systems</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
 
        <article class="project-card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-meta">
              <span class="card-type">Project</span>
              <span class="card-date">January 2026</span>
            </div>
            <span class="card-glyph">⟁</span>
          </div>
          <h3>2-DOF Excavator Payload Mechanism</h3>
          <p>Designed a 3D-printed excavator-style payload system in Fusion 360 with two actuated joints (elbow, wrist). Created custom printed bearings and gears; integrated high-torque servos with bearing-supported pivot points to reduce friction.</p>
          <ul class="card-tags">
            <li>Fusion 360</li><li>Servo Actuation</li><li>Mechanical Design</li><li>3D Printing</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
 
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
 
